          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
            <a href="/contact/" class="bg-[#E8A317] text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-yellow-600 text-center transition-colors">Get a Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:+12485222573" class="border border-white text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-[#1B3A5C] text-center transition-colors">(248) 522-2573</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
